Usage: loadLefFile [-help] [<file1 file2 ...>] [-areaIo] [-blackbox]
                   [-incremental]

-help                                   # Prints out the command usage
<file1 file2 ...>                       # Lef file(s) to load
                                        # (string, optional)
-areaIo                                 # Treats the pad macro cell as an
                                        # areaIo cell (bool, optional)
-blackbox                               # Treats the block macro cell as a
                                        # blackbox (bool, optional)
-incremental                            # Replace the antenna data into
                                        # existing layers and macro cells
                                        # (bool, optional)